              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="my-40">
        <div class="container">
          <h2 id="sponsors" class="text-6xl">Our beloved Sponsors</h2>
          <div class="space-content mt-20 text-lg">
            <p>
              The conference could not happen without their support to the community! They help make the conference
              affordable and share the values of developing maintainable software. This 2-day unconference is a perfect
              moment to talk authentically with them.
            </p>
            <p class="font-bold">
              If you want to be a sponsor, <a
                href="mailto:nicolascarlo.espeon@gmail.com?subject=SoCraTes CA 2024 sponsorship"
                >reach out (nicolascarlo.espeon@gmail.com)</a
              > to get the details.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
